.TH DAIP 1 "2026-01-02" "dumbass-tree" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
daip \- iproute2 helper (brief status + explain scary tokens)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B daip
<command>
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B brief
Show ip -br addr and brief routes.
.TP
.B cheat
Print the 90% iproute2 cheat sheet.
.TP
.B explain <words...>
Explain common tokens like 'scope global dynamic master'.
